      <title>०२३ प्रजाव्याकुलता</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/mahAbhAratam/vyAsaH/goraxapura-pAThaH/hindy-anuvAdaH/03_vanaparva/03_arjunAbhigamanaparva/02_munyupadeshaH/023_prajAvyAkulatA/</link>
